#: ../../user_interface/menu/settings_menu/configure_kdenlive.rst:143
msgid ""
"**Proxy Clips - Concurrent Threads**  This will set the number of threads "
"the program will attempt to use when calling ffmpeg to encode :ref:`clips`. "
"This will be what kdenlive passes to the ffmpeg  *-threads* parameter. "
"Increasing this parameter may not have an effect if you have changed the "
"proxy encoding settings using :ref:`project_settings` to a codec that ffmpeg "
"does not do multi-thread on. (Multi-threading is supported for MPEG-2, "
"MPEG-4, H.264, and VP8)"
msgstr ""
"**Clips intermediaris - Fils concurrents** Això definirà el nombre de fils "
"que el programa intentarà usar en cridar el «ffmpeg» per a codificar :ref:"
"`clips`. El Kdenlive passarà això al paràmetre *-threads* del «ffmpeg». "
"Incrementar aquest paràmetre pot no tenir cap efecte si heu canviat la "
"configuració de codificació dels intermediaris usant :ref:`project_settings` "
"a un còdec que el «ffmpeg» no el tracti com a multifil. (El multifil està "
"implementat per a MPEG-2, MPEG-4, H.264, i VP8)"

#: ../../user_interface/menu/settings_menu/configure_kdenlive.rst:147
#| msgid ""
#| "**Processing threads**: This is experimental and was removed in ver "
#| "0.9.10. This number was passed to melts *real_time* consumer property. "
#| "This parameter increases the number of threads the program uses for video "
#| "decoding and processing (but not encoding which is controlled via :ref:"
#| "`render`).  See `mlt doco <http://www.mltframework.org/bin/view/MLT/"
#| "Questions#Does_MLT_take_advantage_of_multi>`_. Using this has potential "
#| "side effects - see `this <https://forum.kde.org/viewtopic.php?f=265&amp;"
#| "t=122140#p317318>`_ forum post from the author of the Melt program."
msgid ""
"**Processing and transcode jobs**: This is experimental and was removed in "
"ver 0.9.10. This number was passed to melts *real_time* consumer property. "
"This parameter increases the number of threads the program uses for video "
"decoding and processing (but not encoding which is controlled via :ref:"
"`render`).  See `mlt doco <https://www.mltframework.org/faq/#does-mlt-take-"
"advantage-of-multiple-cores-or-how-do-i-enable-parallel-processing>`_. Using "
"this has potential side effects - see `this <https://forum.kde.org/viewtopic."
"php?f=265&t=122140#p317318>`_ forum post from the author of the Melt program."
msgstr ""
"**Treballs de processament i transcodificació**: Això era experimental i es"
" va eliminar a la ver. 0.9.10. Aquest nombre es passava per a fusionar la"
" propietat de consum *temps real*. Aquest paràmetre incrementa el nombre de"
" fils que usa el programa per a descodificar vídeo i processar (però no per a"
" codificar, que es controla :ref:`render`). Vegeu la `documentació del «mlt»"
" <https://www.mltframework.org/faq/#does-mlt-take-advantage-of-multiple-cores-"
"or-how-do-i-enable-parallel-processing>`_. El seu ús té efectes col·laterals"
" potencials: vegeu `aquest <https://forum.kde.org/viewtopic.php?f=265&t=122140"
"#p317318>`_ article del fòrum de l'autor del programa Melt."

